## Bank manipulation
Create, Update, Find Bank
return @void

> Example request:

```bash
curl -X GET "http://classy.pos/Api/V1/Banks/Bank/List" \
-H "Accept: application/json"
```

```javascript
var settings = {
    "async": true,
    "crossDomain": true,
    "url": "http://classy.pos/Api/V1/Banks/Bank/List",
    "method": "GET",
    "headers": {
        "accept": "application/json"
    }
}

$.ajax(settings).done(function (response) {
    console.log(response);
});
```
